Detailed Description

Bi-partitioning Constraints Management Base Class. Mainly to answer question "Is a vertex allowed to move from one partition to another?"

bool BiConstrMgrBase::satisfiedAll ( const int *  diff) [inline]
Returns:
true if current status is OK. In the current implement, only need to check the cell area constraint (cell weight). In the future, we may add other constraints such as #terminal on each partition.
